    <div class="container">
        <!-- Title -->
        <h1>Real Estate Listing Platform Development Project</h1>
        <p class="lead">An exciting opportunity to create a dynamic platform for real estate listings, demonstrating skills in web development, database management, and UI design.</p>

        <!-- Problem Description -->
        <section>
            <h2>Problem Description</h2>
            <p>Your task is to develop an online platform where users can list, browse, and search for real estate properties. The platform should be user-friendly and handle essential functionalities expected from a real estate website.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Steps to Follow -->
        <section>
            <h2>Steps to Follow</h2>

            <!-- Requirement Analysis -->
            <h3>1. Requirement Analysis</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Define the platform's scope, including different <strong>user roles</strong> (e.g., buyers, sellers, agents).</li>
                <li>Identify key features: property listings, search functionality, image galleries, and contact forms.</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Technology Selection -->
            <h3>2. Technology Selection</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Select the <strong>tech stack</strong> (e.g., HTML, CSS, JavaScript) for both front-end and back-end development.</li>
                <li>Choose frameworks and libraries to streamline development and improve performance.</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Database Design -->
            <h3>3. Database Design</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Design a <strong>database schema</strong> to store property listings and user data effectively.</li>
                <li>Ensure scalability to accommodate complex queries and a growing dataset.</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Front-End Development -->
            <h3>4. Front-End Development</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Create an intuitive and visually appealing <strong>user interface</strong>.</li>
                <li>Implement a responsive design to ensure accessibility across all devices.</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Testing and Deployment -->
            <h3>5. Testing and Deployment</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Perform thorough testing, covering functionality, usability, and performance.</li>
                <li>Deploy the platform on a <strong>reliable web server</strong> for public access.</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Documentation and Maintenance -->
            <h3>6. Documentation and Maintenance</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Document the development process, including any challenges and their solutions.</li>
                <li>Plan for ongoing maintenance and periodic updates.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Additional Notes -->
        <section>
            <h2>Additional Notes</h2>
            <p>For detailed guidance on each step, refer to the blog and reference materials provided. This project will highlight your technical skills and ability to manage end-to-end web development processes for a real-world application.</p>
        </section>
